        <titleType>Display Title</titleType>
        <title>Drug Trafficking Vessel Interdiction Act of 2008</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 18, United States Code, to prohibit operation by any means or embarking in any submersible or semi-submersible vessel that is without nationality and that is navigating or has navigated into, through or from waters beyond the outer limit of the territorial sea of a single country or a lateral limit of that country's territorial sea with an adjacent country, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Titles as Amended by House</titleType>
        <title>To enhance drug trafficking interdiction by creating a Federal felony relating to operating or embarking in a submersible or semi-submersible vessel without nationality and on an international voyage.</title>
        <chamberCode>H</chamberCode>
        <chamberName>House</chamberName>
      </item>
